---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy policy"
  description="How Produto com IA collects, uses, protects and deletes data submitted to receive free resources."
  lang="en"
  alternateUrl="/privacidade/"
>
  <article class="container article-body" style="padding-top:4rem;padding-bottom:4rem">
    <h1>Privacy policy</h1>
    <p><strong>Notice version:</strong> 2026-07-22. <strong>Last reviewed:</strong> July 22, 2026.</p>

    <h2>Who controls the data</h2>
    <p>Produto com IA, under the responsibility of Rodrigo Tozato, is the controller of the data described on this page. For questions or requests, email <a href="mailto:rodrigo.tozato@icloud.com">rodrigo.tozato@icloud.com</a>.</p>

    <h2>What we collect and why</h2>
    <p>When you request a free resource, we collect your email, your choice to receive or decline updates, the requested resource, source page, language, and request date and time. We use this data to deliver the file, recognize your browser for future downloads, protect the service against abuse and keep an operational delivery record.</p>
    <p>Marketing updates are optional, unchecked by default and never required for the download. You can receive the resource without authorizing marketing messages.</p>

    <h2>Providers and processing</h2>
    <p>We use <strong>Cloudflare Turnstile</strong> to reduce automated submissions and <strong>Resend</strong> to send the owner an operational notification for each download. These providers may process data outside Brazil through their own infrastructure and policies. We do not sell your data or share it for third-party advertising.</p>

    <h2>Retention and security</h2>
    <p>Lead and download records are retained for up to <strong>730 days</strong>, unless a different period is required to meet an applicable obligation or legitimate request. Recognition sessions expire sooner. We use restricted access, protected connections, anti-abuse validation and secrets kept out of public code; no system can eliminate every risk.</p>

    <h2>Your requests</h2>
    <p>You may request confirmation and access to your data, correction of incomplete or inaccurate information, withdrawal of consent for updates, and deletion of records that can be removed. Email <a href="mailto:rodrigo.tozato@icloud.com">rodrigo.tozato@icloud.com</a> from the address submitted in the form so we can locate and protect your record.</p>

    <h2>Changes</h2>
    <p>We may update this notice when the service changes. The version and review date at the top of the page identify the text applicable to a registration.</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
